          "date": "2014-03-24 16:42:26.000000000",
          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-4584 mdt: ensure orig lock is found in hash upon resend",
        "message": "LU-4584 mdt: ensure orig lock is found in hash upon resend\n\nLook for 1st lock found in hash for remote_hdl but that's noti\nnew_lock itself.\nThere should only be 2 upon resent, new_lock and the 1st/orig\none we want ...\n\nAlso add a ref on it again like when just created!\n\nSince it is master patch version where patch for LU-4403 has\nalready landed, I had to remove its too restrictive optimization\nand allow implicit layout_lock upon open handling upon resend. But\nI left its [un]lock_res_and_lock() protection it introduced, even\nif I am not convinced it is required in this case.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5d0b47d85f62437d2915294a72e2802ab3ed80e0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
